author: Joseph Wulfsohn
title: CNN analyst mocked for claiming it's a 'GOP campaign message' to blame China for virus outbreak
description: CNN political analyst Nathan Gonzales was mocked on Wednesday for suggesting that casting blame onto China for the coronavirus outbreak is becoming a "GOP campaign message."
